data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Come Home to this 2 Acre Waterfront Estate on Beautiful Lake Harris. Enter through the Private Gate to a winding tree-lined Paved driveway.  The primary home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms (2353 Sq FT) The detached mother-in-law suite offers 2 bedrooms, high ceilings, tile floors, lots of storage, and is light and bright, also 1 bath (600+ sq ft) and an oversized 2 car garage. In the primary home, you will find a Spacious living room, lots of natural light, Bamboo Floors, and a mini-split A/C. The large kitchen is in the center of the home with Corian countertops, Stainless Steel appliances, and a Garden Window. The Delightful formal dining room adjoins the kitchen with Crown Molding, Custom Wood built-ins, and a Wood-burning Fireplace. The family room has a stunning Lake View and sliding doors that open to the Florida room.  The Master Suite showcases a large Jetted Tub with a Double Vanity,  Walk-in Shower,  Cathedral Ceiling, and a Walk-in Closet leading to the laundry room. Don't miss the Separate Workshop and Full RV hook-up. The backyard is Your own private oasis with Century-Old Oaks and Fruit-bearing Trees. You can take a nice stroll down to Your Private Boat Dock for all the enjoyment that The Chain Of Lakes has to offer. NO HOA's
